{"tid":46932,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"只想單身一個","createTime":"2016-12-20T04:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T07:14:10.000Z","uid":24030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6fe901c8026c6e0485c9d4342cef88727b5a4e","tid":46932,"uid":24030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:16:27.000Z","msg":"幾年前同A曖昧好耐，但到最後無疾而終，再加上個時壓力比較大，搞到自己抑鬱<br />\n就係咁樣記起心上好耐好耐，條友又要keep住傾計但又相比以前冷淡左好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n期間有第二個追，但都發現完全無feel，愛唔落<br />\n仲要臨近聖誕約去倒數，其實我好想自己一個<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直留係上一段戀情 move on唔到 <br />\n寧願自己一個都唔想再搵新對象<br />\n聖誕喎，希望你返工唔好再咁攰，多啲休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294a11bc3cee2748a31a73b5b538cff6d12a891e","tid":46932,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:17:53.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"f8224d3eb6e2c8d86ff6251a09378205dffe5f2f","tid":46932,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"對我黎講好奢侈<br />\n有人追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係自己杯茶 但起碼証明左自己有市場"},{"pid":"3732be1f46b71048e93366450fb3c66b54f9070b","tid":46932,"uid":24030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對我黎講好奢侈<br />\n有人追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係自己杯茶 但起碼証明左自己有市場</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當你發現你個人得返個殼，你會覺得這些都原算什麼<br />\n利申唔靚"},{"pid":"ac2c0efe4f1304ab4be4919a350959a8d1969f29","tid":46932,"uid":24030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對我黎講好奢侈<br />\n有人追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔係自己杯茶 但起碼証明左自己有市場</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當你發現你個人得返個殼，你會覺得這些都原算什麼<br />\n利申唔靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不算*<img src=\"/assets/f